
1) Generate the Makefile:

./config.sh FLAG1 FLAG2 ...

FLAGS may be:

INIT_ICE_FROM_FILE
INIT_ICE_RANDOM
INIT_ICE_FOURIER
INIT_ICE_SINGLEMODE
MECHANICAL_CORRELATED
MELT_PONDS
INIT_MELT_PONDS_FROM_FILE
MELTING_LUETHJE
MELTING_WETTLAUFER
WIND_SHEAR
LATERAL_DRAINAGE
SEEPAGE_CONSTANT
SEEPAGE_DARCY
VOLUMETRIC_FLUXES 

2) Generate the executable (sea-ice)

make sea-ice

3) Run

./sea-ice input



